  <div class="AreaR">
    <div class="box">
     <div class="box_1">
      <div style="border:4px solid #fcf8f7; background-color:#fff; padding:20px 15px;">
         <div class="tc" style="padding:8px;">
         <font class="f5 f6">产品理念</font><br /><font class="f3">卡卡鲜在线配菜 / 2012-11-06</font>
         </div>
                   <p><span style="font-size: medium"><img alt="" width="700" height="100" src="http://kakaxian.com/images/upload/Image/asdasd454465.jpg" />&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="line-height: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif"><span style="color: rgb(0,128,128)"><span style="font-size: x-large">健康 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">1、我们定点采购，确保菜源健康；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">2、我们严格按照流程清洗食材，去除蔬菜农药残留；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">3、我们所有人员，包括配送人员，全部体检，持有健康证。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">4、我们当日采购，当日送达，绝无过夜食材；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">5、我们做成半成品，您在家自行烹饪，告别地沟油和不清洁餐具。</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 72pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-line-height-alt: 11.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="font-size: x-large"><span style="line-height: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif"><span style="color: rgb(0,128,128)">便捷</span></span></span></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">1、我们把食材买好、洗好、切好、配好、加上作料、配上菜谱、您在家可直接下锅烹饪；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">2、稍复杂一些的菜品，食材我们的厨师师傅已做了卫生、专业的粗加工，比如&ldquo;粉蒸肉&ldquo;（粉蒸小排、梅干菜扣肉），肉已完全调制好，直接上锅蒸熟即可吃，比如&ldquo;回锅肉&rdquo;，肉已用水煮熟，可直接烹饪；含肉丝、肉片的荤菜，肉我们已酱过，等等；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">3、除了油盐这类家中常备的作料，其他作料（如葱、姜、蒜、色拉、香料等等）我们已为您备好；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">4、已用干净的食品包装袋（量大我们会采用环保的帆布袋）包装好，直接送到您手里（家或者办公室）；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">5、菜品我们已分类包装好，贴上&ldquo;配料标签&rdquo;、&ldquo;菜谱标签&rdquo;，最大限度的方便您烹饪。</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraph" style="text-indent: -36pt; margin-left: 108pt; mso-char-indent-count: 0; mso-line-height-alt: 11.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1">&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="font-size: medium"><span style="line-height: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif"><span style="color: rgb(0,128,128)"><span style="font-size: x-large">营养</span></span></span></span></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">1，我们不只卖&ldquo;净菜&rdquo;，更注重营养搭配，膳食调理；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">2，我们持续关注各种营养知识，并实践在我们的菜品里；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">3，我们不断的推出各种营养系列，如，修身纤体，提神养颜，秋冬进补，暑夏清凉，孕妇亲子等等；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">4，我们不断改进营养搭配，降低&ldquo;三高&rdquo;食材；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">5，推出套餐，引导大家注重持续、合理的营养搭配和膳食习惯。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h1><span style="font-size: x-large"><span style="line-height: 11pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif"><span style="color: rgb(0,128,128)">时尚</span></span></span></h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">1、卡卡和他的朋友们，都是80后，他们都向往新的Life Style；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">2、告别垃圾食品，回归家庭，享受生活，这本身就是一种年轻人的时尚；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">3、微博（&ldquo;卡卡鲜&rdquo;）、微信（&ldquo;卡卡鲜&rdquo;和&ldquo;卡卡鲜yoyo&rdquo;）、手机APP均可找到卡卡鲜，我们随时在各个渠道与您交流和互动；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">4、环保是一种时尚。您购买量大（40元以上），送货地址是公司（带回家去烹饪），我们用精致的环保帆布袋包装，里面装的是菜，外面看上去像是Zara出品；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">5、为了更贴近白领，卡卡鲜将推出欧美、东南亚的菜品，让大家DIY外国菜。</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: medium">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>                           <div style="padding:8px; margin-top:15px; text-align:left; border-top:1px solid #ccc;">
         
